&quot; what happened this morning was that the baton of Lesotho &apos;s defense forces acted after receiving several intelligence reports that within the police some elements that actually wanted to arm some of the political , bipartisan young fanatics who were about to cause devastating harm , &quot; he said to Voice of America .
