at the weekend there were protests from opponents of the Nato summit in Newport .
on Saturday , hundreds gathered at the center of Newport for an anti @-@ NATO march .
on Sunday , about 150 people arrived in Cardiff in front of the city hall to hold a so @-@ called counter @-@ summit .
